Technology used:

Python  ---> Python 3.6 Version
Pygame  ---> pip install pygame


Algorithm to be implemented :

A* Algo to optimize the solution.

About 8 Number Puzzle:

Puzzle having 9 tiles present in grid of 3X3. These tiles are having random numbers from 1 to 8 and No.9 Tile to be blank 'space'. You need to re-arrange them in sorted order from 1 to 8 followed by 9. Important thing you can only swap the digit horizontally or vertically with the blank tile.

What this project does?

It generates the random puzzle, which user can play. And also at any time he can click on the solve button to solve the existing puzzle.

What you have to do ?

Implement the code when user click on  solve button

Run the code:

Run puzzle.py file to run the code.